a for the library API.\\n\\n## Action taken\\n\\nRemoved the non-metadata failing generated test and its test-only support:\\n\\n- deleted `tests/src/javax.activation/javax.activation-api/1.2.0/src/test/java/javax_activation/javax_activation_api/SecuritySupport2Test.java`\\n- deleted `tests/src/javax.activation/javax.activation-api/1.2.0/src/test/resources/META-INF/mimetypes.default`\\n- removed the extra test-jar packaging block from `tests/src/javax.activation/javax.activation-api/1.2.0/build.gradle`\\n\\n## Why the remaining generated support should be preserved\\n\\nThe remaining generated support still covers meaningful native-image behaviors for this library and should stay in place:\\n\\n- `CommandInfoBeansTest` exercises `CommandInfo` instantiation through the Beans API.\\n- `MailcapCommandMapTest` exercises dynamic handler loading and fallback class loading paths.\\n- `SecuritySupport4Test` still validates resource enumeration through `SecuritySupport#getSystemResources`.\\n\\nThose tests represent real library behavior and were successful in the native run, so the remaining generated support is still useful and should be preserved.\"\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge4/metadata-forge/local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/2123-3b33bb3d/script_run_metrics/add_new_library_support.json:4711:      \"iterations\": 6,\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge4/metadata-forge/local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/2123-3b33bb3d/script_run_metrics/add_new_library_support.json:4713:      \"generated_loc\": 150,\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge4/metadata-forge/local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/2123-3b33bb3d/script_run_metrics/add_new_library_support.json:4716:      \"code_coverage_percent\": 15.14\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge4/metadata-forge/local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/2123-3b33bb3d/script_run_metrics/add_new_library_support.json:4731:    \"status\": \"success\",\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge4/metadata-forge/local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/2123-3b33bb3d/script_run_metrics/add_new_library_support.json: